{"tid":2220230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[驚世文] 網購中秋果籃","createTime":"2020-09-27T13:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T05:45:34.000Z","uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8ea4124e13a9b03f15935cec8e309238679f9d","tid":2220230,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n成波之路幫間生果店LC Fruit賣廣告<br />\n有眼利既巴絲打見到個蜜瓜貨不對板啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（Set寫 「日本糖瓏蜜瓜」但糖瓏瓜根本就係支那野）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQ4QD5g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQ4QD5g.png&h=15350b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n店主就拿拿林say sorry 承認錯誤<br />\n安排退款之餘<br />\n仲將個糖瓏蜜瓜改做日本雷電赤肉蜜瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4g7GjS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4g7GjS.png&h=d7fb7449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是我就信左佢，落左訂，因為想食日本瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到送貨前一日我就收到whatsapp話佢地失預算<br />\n來貨價太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以取消所有訂單同安排退錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HhZExtP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHhZExtP.png&h=6297ff81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事關我做孝子諗住同屋企人一齊食<br />\n問下佢地有冇其他果籃代替啦<br />\n對比如下：<br />\n原本有： <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUhrcAz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUhrcAz.png&h=222a94e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家得返：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzC6W2E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzC6W2E.png&h=4eb21591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無左日本蜜瓜 藍莓 日本桃 西瓜<br />\n用兩隻韓國梨代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />錯一次 都算啦<br />\n錯多一次唔好玩各位巴絲啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d511f675d4973614ffe1b795b982fba4cb883d6","tid":2220230,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2217996/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2217996/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f49aa84a4d57739c69185ab80f17f87265b8e9c0","tid":2220230,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d511f675d4973614ffe1b795b982fba4cb883d6","tid":2220230,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2217996/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2217996/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早啲有呢個post我就唔洗中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5222be9af4f5d676d16006122c66cf67d85f59","tid":2220230,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}